      "writtenOn": "2018-05-11T13:37:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "IIUC \"nextIndex\" is the *unfetched* next index. Since the terminal index is the *last* index in the log stream (i.e., a valid index), we are only finished if \"nextIndex\" is \u003e lst.TerminalIndex, not \u003e\u003d.",
      "range": {
